March 8, 2021 / The investigation into Thomas Lee Dillon ended once he confessed to the murder of five outdoorsmen in Ohio – but did he really confess to every crime that he had committed, or could there have been some that he left out?

Episode scoring music by Animal Weapon and Blue Dot Sessions.
